<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Favorite Book Corner</h1>
    <p>Explore your favorite genres, read authentic reviews, and find new reading inspiration.</p>
    <a href="#genres" class="btn btn-primary">Discover Now</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="genres" class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Featured Genres</h2>
  </div>
  <div id="genre-list" class="genre-grid">
    {{#if categories.length}}
    {{#each categories}}
    <div class="genre-item genre-card-wrapper">

      <section class="genre-card">
        <div class="genre-meta">
          <span class="chip">{{this.name}}</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="book-strip">
            {{#if books.length}}
            {{#each this.books}}
            <a class="book-card" href="/sach/{{this.slug}}">
              {{!-- <div class="cover" aria-hidden="true"></div> --}}
              <img class="cover" src="/api/image/{{this._id}}" alt="{{this.slug}}">
              <div class="book-body">
                <h3 class="title">{{this.title}}</h3>
                <p class="author">{{this.author}}</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            {{/each}}
            {{/if}}
          </div>
          <div class="card-actions">
            {{!-- <span class="muted">${genre.description || ''}</span> --}}
            <a class="btn see-more" href="/category/{{this.slug}}">See More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    {{/each}}
    {{else}}
    <div class="no-categories-message">
      <span>Chưa có sách nào ở đây, đang chuẩn bị những cuốn sách thú vị cho bạn!</span>
    </div>
    {{/if}}

  </div>
</section>

<section class="fun-section">
  <div class="fun-content">
    <h2>Book Thoughts & Fun</h2>
    <p>Some little reflections, fun insights, and thoughts about my favorite stories.</p>

    <div class="fun-cards">
      <div class="fun-card">
        <h3>Reflection</h3>
        <p>Every story leaves a tiny mark. Sometimes it’s a phrase, sometimes a feeling I can’t forget.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="fun-card">
        <h3>Mini Insight</h3>
        <p>Characters often teach more than plots. A clever twist in dialogue can stay in mind for days.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="fun-card">
        <h3>Reading Mood</h3>
        <p>Some books I revisit just for the atmosphere. Cozy, mysterious, or thrilling — each has its charm.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="fun-card">
        <h3>Fun Note</h3>
        <p>Sometimes the best stories are the ones I imagine myself continuing after the last page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


