  <div class="fun-content">
    <h2>Book Reflections & Notes</h2>
    <p>Little thoughts and reflections on the stories I love.</p>

    <div class="zigzag-cards">
      <div class="zigzag-card left">
        <h3>Favorite Characters</h3>
        <p>Characters with depth always stay with me, even after finishing the story.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="zigzag-card right">
        <h3>Plot Twists I Loved</h3>
        <p>Unexpected turns that made me pause and think about the story differently.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="zigzag-card left">
        <h3>Atmosphere</h3>
        <p>Some books have a mood so vivid I can almost step into their world.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="zigzag-card right">
        <h3>Memorable Quotes</h3>
        <p>Lines that linger in my mind and make me reflect on life or imagination.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="zigzag-card left">
        <h3>Mini Lessons</h3>
        <p>Even short stories can teach something meaningful or spark new ideas.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="zigzag-card right">
        <h3>Fun Thoughts</h3>
        <p>Sometimes I imagine alternate endings or what characters would do next.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>